{"tid":2122791,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"17歲男生認藏行山杖錘子等判感化1年 法庭相信被告是出於關心社會才會做出超越法律的行為","createTime":"2020-07-24T07:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T09:08:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"de346bc6f1bc54c1f1ff5e959a3a3401be657d4f","tid":2122791,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:55:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F7342&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6Kix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=71817f8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7342</a><br />\n<br />\n#沙田裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#溫紹明署理主任裁判官 <br />\n#判刑<br />\n#1112馬鞍山<br />\n<br />\n呂(17)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)管有適合作非法用途的工具<br />\n(2)管有任何物品意圖毀或損壞財產<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n(1)被控於19年11月12日在馬鞍山德信中學外管有適合作非法用途的工具，即一支尖的鐵枝、一支削尖的行山杖<br />\n(2)被控於同日同地保管一支槌子及一支破碎玻璃用的槌子，意圖使用物品摧毁他人財產<br />\n<br />\n上一堂裁判官考慮到被告年輕、初犯、坦白認罪等因素，決定索取感化及社會服務令報告後才判刑。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師指出感化報告建議判處12個月感化令，指被告有真誠悔意；並呈上其DSE成績，多科考獲4級成績，很大可能會獲得大學收錄。<br />\n<br />\n判決：<br />\n法庭相信被告是出於關心社會才會做出超越法律的行為；又指被告已經付出代價，會有刑事紀錄。法庭知悉被告有不俗的DSE成績，希望被告可以繼續讀書，重新開始人生並在將來貢獻社會。因而接納感化報告的建議，判被告12個月感化令，兩項控罪刑罰同期執行。"},{"pid":"6dd8afdd866b723e8122d43a02dbab40b897b92d","tid":2122791,"uid":214502,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"今日d官 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f17e69ac6ab0a78af439bd9968ad7b831fdb1e","tid":2122791,"uid":238920,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:56:26.000Z","msg":"唔洗坐已經算好<br />\n起碼冇再俾人告就冇案底"},{"pid":"16a7728702101d2e20f998896f6f1256a9c75132","tid":2122791,"uid":181502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6dd8afdd866b723e8122d43a02dbab40b897b92d","tid":2122791,"uid":214502,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"今日d官 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"今日星期五嘛"},{"pid":"79302298465896bb7e42933ce8000d847199d6e6","tid":2122791,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:57:02.000Z","msg":"感乜撚嘢化<br />\n<br />\n唔俾帶行山杖出街？<br />\n<br />\n又一紅官"},{"pid":"799c115314ca101af71d0b159262cc6b6d2cc3c4","tid":2122791,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79302298465896bb7e42933ce8000d847199d6e6","tid":2122791,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:57:02.000Z","msg":"感乜撚嘢化<br />\n<br />\n唔俾帶行山杖出街？<br />\n<br />\n又一紅官"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:00:48.000Z","msg":"被告認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6acf635b219ca3ee4adb174696a4e927afd2560","tid":2122791,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79302298465896bb7e42933ce8000d847199d6e6","tid":2122791,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:57:02.000Z","msg":"感乜撚嘢化<br />\n<br />\n唔俾帶行山杖出街？<br />\n<br />\n又一紅官"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"即一支尖的鐵枝、一支削尖的行山杖<br />\n被控於同日同地保管一支槌子及一支破碎玻璃用的槌子"},{"pid":"382e4813b0be5cb3cb8e131ca341a95238f75be5","tid":2122791,"uid":185652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a6acf635b219ca3ee4adb174696a4e927afd2560","tid":2122791,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79302298465896bb7e42933ce8000d847199d6e6","tid":2122791,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:57:02.000Z","msg":"感乜撚嘢化<br />\n<br />\n唔俾帶行山杖出街？<br />\n<br />\n又一紅官"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"即一支尖的鐵枝、一支削尖的行山杖<br />\n被控於同日同地保管一支槌子及一支破碎玻璃用的槌子"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:02:37.000Z","msg":"如果係陳惠敏入梗勞教"},{"pid":"e97a64ee3860b02c2babc73d1018dce50b7aa204","tid":2122791,"uid":150483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"382e4813b0be5cb3cb8e1