ly.com/local/20200724/HJCPWU32776NYGBZOWLPWSNJPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FHJCPWU32776NYGBZOWLPWSNJPU%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6Kix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=076395aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FHJCPWU32776NYGBZOWLPWSNJPU%2F&h=9032c296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200724/HJCPWU32776NYGBZOWLPWSNJPU/</a>"},{"pid":"c58afdc812625cc77e6d6dd61be00dbd3760d967","tid":2122791,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"951f6bff5f7725834144a8aa6623e20b89225bac","tid":2122791,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:21:46.000Z","msg":"署理主任裁判官裁判官溫紹明判刑時指，相信被告因關心社會而超越法律界線，若不是社會事件引發，他可能一生都會奉公守法，遂按感化官建議，判被告接受感化一年。<br />\n<br />\n溫官續指，被告17歲已有定罪紀錄，已付出很大代價，必然上了寶貴一課；若不是社會事件引發本案，被告可能一生都會是奉公守法的人，希望被告在今次事件後重新開始。溫官認為最佳安排是讓被告繼續讀書，令他將來可貢獻社會。基於被告展露悔意且有家庭支援，採納報告建議判處感化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200724/HJCPWU32776NYGBZOWLPWSNJPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FHJCPWU32776NYGBZOWLPWSNJPU%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6Kix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=076395aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FHJCPWU32776NYGBZOWLPWSNJPU%2F&h=9032c296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200724/HJCPWU32776NYGBZOWLPWSNJPU/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=